{"id":356904,"date":[{"year":1957,"month":11,"day":2}],"page":"5","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"体育场","column":"三言两语","genre":"","count":"67","ytitle":"","mtitle":"冷酷的心","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"运动员在运动场中，何以会成为疯子?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为钱卖命也。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可见，美国球坛老板，不仅有‘小狗的想像力’，而且还有一颗冷酷的心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(文)"}]}